imals on their own terms.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aDogsxBehaviorxEvolution. 0aDogs-Behavior-Evolution. 0aDogs-Training. 0aDogs. 7aNATURE / Animals / Mammals.2bisacsh1 aBekoff, Marc, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073912140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780691228969423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780691228969/original  a978-3-11-073912-1  Princeton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK